key

public String key

refData

public CwObject refData
READONLY: Gets the referenced Document from the database. Performs database operations and may have visible negative impact on the application performance

reference

public CwObject reference
READONLY: Gets the referenced document from the document cache. Reads the data object from the database when the document is not found in the cache or when it has been in the cache longer than specified in the reference finder volatility. As the referenced documents are cached in the memory THERE IS POSSIBILITY TO GET STALE DATA THAT DOES NOT MATCH WHAT IS IN THE DATABASE. THE RETURNED DATA DOCUMENT IS IMMUTABLE.
